process.argv kya hai?
process.argv ek array hota hai jo Node.js ke command-line arguments ko store karta hai.

Isme:

process.argv[0] hota hai: node ka path

process.argv[1] hota hai: script file ka path

process.argv[2] se shuru hote hain actual arguments jo tu command line me deta hai


